// Track E — Production Model Governance (README stub, hexa-flavored)
// R1 HEXA-FIRST: keep this file short, no code here; see spec for flow.
// Parent spec: shared/harness/go_tracks/E_production_model.md
// SSOT:       shared/state/production_model_status.json
// Promote:    shared/docs/track_e_promote.hexa (noop placeholder)
//
// Flow (one cycle):
//   1. identify  — read production_model_status.json .current
//   2. verify R2 — rclone ls r2:anima-models/<track>/<run>/<step>/
//   3. compare   — candidate vs current: eval_loss down, phi_holo up, korean 5-turn pass
//   4. promote   — update .current, push old .current into .history[]
//   5. clean     — commit + R2 sha256 verify; never delete ckpts in this track
//
// Hard rules (never violate):
//   - no smoke/debug/test ckpts as production
//   - no promotion without R2 backup verified
//   - no quantization      (see feedback_no_quantization.md)
//   - no version filenames (see feedback_no_version_in_filename.md)
//   - this track owns only metadata; it does NOT modify running training
//     or delete checkpoints
